abstract: Driven column; journalists at Mudfest competition in Washington State pick best sport utility vehicles in six categories.
lead_paragraph: Over two days at this year’s Mudfest in the Pacific Northwest, 26 journalists evaluated 27 vehicles, including crossovers, S.U.V.s and pickups.
